title.en: nubbe: The data model for nubbeDB Knowledge Graph

author: Edgard Marx, Stefan Schmidt-Dichte, Istvan J. Mocsy

description.en: The nubbe Ontology contains the data model of nubbeDB Knowledge Graph. It facilitates the knowledge graph data manipulation and consumption through concepts such as natural products, molecules, and their respective properties.
